#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:None
msgid "Field Cleaning Records dashboard in the Data Cleaning application."
msgstr "لوحة بيانات سجلات تنظيف الحقول في تطبيق تنظيف البيانات."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:335
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`CLEANING RULES` sidebar lists each of the active cleaning "
