"or :ref:`upload files <spreadsheet/get-started/upload-files>` and open them "
"as Odoo spreadsheets"
msgstr ""
":ref:`إنشاء جداول البيانات <spreadsheet/get-started/create-spreadsheet>` أو "
":ref:`تحميل الملفات <spreadsheet/get-started/upload-files>` وفتحها كجداول "
"بيانات Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet.rst:26
